  "instructions": [
    "Blend tofu, soy milk, water, turmeric powder, and chili paste in a blender until smooth.",
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat. Add garlic, onions, carrots, and peppers.",
    "Stir-fry for about 5 minutes until vegetables are slightly softened.",
    "Pour the blended mixture into the pan and stir well to combine.",
    "Simmer for another 10 minutes while stirring occasionally.",
    "Season with salt to taste."
